Commentary: full on off, but the ball stays low. Hope defends off the bat's toe end. Played to mid on
Commentary_short: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Hope, no run

Commentary: good length outside of, but turning away after pitching. Cut to point
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to KOA Powell, no run

Commentary: full on leg, and he misses the sweep. Hits his front leg and the ball trickles down to short fine leg. They take a single, and the throw misses the stumps! Chance of overthrows, but the fielder's backing up
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to KOA Powell, 1 leg bye

Commentary: full just outside off. Hope comes forward to defend, and squirts a shot to the leg side. Moves to 49
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to Hope, 1 run

Commentary: good length on leg,and Powell walks down the wicket. But he punches it straight to the diving midwicket fielder
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to KOA Powell, no run

Commentary: uses his feet again, and this full ball is drilled down to long on for a single
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to KOA Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full outside off, but spinning inwards sharply! Surprises Hope, but he manages to carve a punch to the off side
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to Hope, no run

Commentary: dropped at long on! Sabbir the guilty man this time. It's a full ball which Powell chips over the non-striker. Sabbir does the hard work, and dives forward too, but just can't hold on to the catch
Commentary_short: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to KOA Powell, 1 run

Commentary: tossed up on middle, and Hope flicks this past the diving midwicket fielder. Fifty for Hope!
Commentary_short: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Hope, 1 run

Commentary: aimed on leg stump, and shoveled to Mashrafe at midwicket. Indecision from the batsman, as they say yes-no-yes-no, and Mortaza has a shy at the non-striker's stumps. But he misses
Commentary_short: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to KOA Powell, 1 run

Commentary: appeal for lbw turned down! Length ball on middle, and spinning into his pads
Commentary_short: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Hope, no run

Commentary: full just outside off, and Hope drives to cover. But this time Powell is already halfway down the wicket with Hope still at the keeper's end. No chance of a single, as Mashrafe collects, lobs the ball to Mehidy, and he wastes no time in whipping the bails off
Commentary_short: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Hope, OUT
Dismissal_text: KOA Powell run out (Mashrafe Mortaza/Mehidy Hasan Miraz) 4 (7b 0x4 0x6) SR: 57.14

Commentary: lands on off stump, and Hope goes onto the back foot to clip it square
Commentary_short: Mehidy Hasan Miraz to Hope, 1 run

Commentary: full and wide outside off. Hope misses the square drive, but the ball finishes inside the tramlines. Dot ball
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to Hope, no run

Commentary: full outside off again, and cut away to point. Finds the fielder once again
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to Hope, no run

Commentary: full on middle, and defended to the leg side with soft hands. They walk across for one. Required-run rate over 10.50 now
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to Hope, 1 run

Commentary: length ball on off, and he muscles a punch off the back foot to the leg side
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: tossed up on off, and angling into Hope. He crunches a punch to the fielder at deep extra cover
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to Hope, 1 run

Commentary: thumped to the cow-corner boundary! Full on off, and he slogs across the line to deep midwicket
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to R Powell, FOUR runs

Commentary: full just outside off, and driven away to deep extra cover. Work for Sabbir in the deep, but his diving effort ensures it's not a boundary. Every run saved counts...
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to Hope, 2 runs

Commentary: full just outside off, and he pushes to cover with soft hands
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to Hope, 1 run

Commentary: back of a length on middle, and angling into his body. Tries to punch to the on side, but the ball goes through to hit his thigh pad. Mortaza appeals for lbw, but not given
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, no run

Commentary: rolls his fingers over this delivery. Much slower, and lands outside off. Tentatively fended away to the off side
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, no run

Commentary: good length outside off, and pulled over midwicket! The infielder may have gotten fingertips to it, and that saves the boundary, because the ball's pace slows down considerably. Mehidy the fielder
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 2 runs

Commentary: slower ball, full outside off. Tapped to cover off the front foot, and he'll retain the strike
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: good length on off, but angling across the batsman. Creams a cut shot off the back foot, but goes straight to Mehidy
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, no run

Commentary: full outside off, and the angle away from Powell forces him to miss the shot. Tries to drive but misses completely
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, no run

Commentary: slashed past the keeper! Full outside off again, and the drive takes a top edge through to the third-man boundary
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, FOUR runs

Commentary: good length on leg stump, but Powell comes down the wicket. Eventually tapped down the ground to long on
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: length ball on leg stump, but Hope walks across to the off side and whips this off his pads, and over square leg for four. Exquisite
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, FOUR runs

Commentary: good length outside off, but this ball stays low! Hope tries to drag a pull from outside off but misses
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, no run

Commentary: good length outside off, and pulled down the ground to long on
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: slower ball full outside off, and the drive to cover is misfielded by the infielder! Shakib the guilty man this time, but thankfully (for Bangladesh) there's someone at long off
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to Hope, 2 runs

Commentary: slower ball again, and this is disguised much better. Hope flicks it away to the leg side, but the ball takes a leading edge and lands safely beyond midwicket. Excellent skill from the Bangladesh captain
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to Hope, 1 run

Commentary: good length on middle, but angling into the batsman. He mistimes a pull to the fielder in the deep, and Powell has enough time to call for the second
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 2 runs

Commentary: full outside off, and Powell's attempted slog takes the inside edge! Beats the stumps, and the keeper, but short fine leg does well to bring the ball back
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 2 runs

Commentary: full outside off, and Powell muscles a shot to long on. Uses the bottom hand to lift it over the non-striker
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full outside off, but Powell already walks across to the pitch of the delivery before driving over cover. Slices this shot over the infield
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full outside off, but deceived by the change-up delivery! Goes for the drive over cover, but the ball goes past his outside edge
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, no run

Commentary: full outside off, but Hope walks across to the off side (exposing all three stumps), trying to flick it behind square. The ball hits the inside of his bat, goes between his legs, and eventually ends up in the keeper's gloves
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, no run

Commentary: full outside off, and he throws his hands at it. The drive takes another top edge through to third man
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, 1 run

Commentary: takes the screws off this! How powerful was that. Just a bit too full outside off, and Powell clears his front leg before tonking this over cow corner
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, SIX runs

Commentary: full outside off, and Powell misses the drive. The ball goes over the tramlines and the umpire calls wide. Mushfiqur isn't happy, probably because the batsman moved to the off side too
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, 1 wide

Commentary: the extra ball goes for four! Low full toss outside off, and Powell drills this past the non-striker for a boundary. Almost takes Hope with him to the ropes too. Raw power.
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, FOUR runs

Commentary: holes out at deep midwicket! Shakib gets under this, and finally Bangladesh hold onto a catch. The offcutter from Mashrafe enticed Hope to go for a big shot, but the slog is not timed well enough
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to Hope, OUT
Dismissal_text: SD Hope c Shakib Al Hasan b Mashrafe Mortaza 64 (94b 5x4 0x6) SR: 68.08

Commentary: full on off, and Powell's attempted drive comes off the inside edge. Trickles down to deep square leg
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full on off, and pushed to long on. Gets off the mark, and wants a double too, but that ain't happening
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to Holder, 1 run

Commentary: slower ball, full on off stump. Pushed down the ground again to long on, but only for a single. Bangladesh won't mind these. Not one bit
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full just outside off, and Holder defends into the gap near cover to steal a single
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to Holder, 1 run

Commentary: slow and wide outside off stump. Powell drags a flat-batted shot down the ground to long on. He'll keep strike
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: knee-high full toss outside off, and Powell check-punches a slog over cow corner! No real followthrough of the bat. Just brute force. Excellent start to the over from West Indies
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, SIX runs

Commentary: full outside of, and he misses out on this slog. Drills a shot into his own boots as the ball dribbles away to the leg side
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full outside off, and the drive is sliced to Mehidy at point. Quick work from the fielder, as he has a shy at the stumps. Misses, but the quick work forces the batsmen to say no to the single
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Holder, 1 run

Commentary: yorker outside off, and Powell's attempted jab takes the inside edge to the leg side
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full outside off, and driven square off the front foot to the fielder at deep point. Just a single. Good comeback from Fizz after that six off the first ball
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Holder, 1 run

Commentary: no he can't! Full on off, and it's in Powell's arc again. Launches this over long on, and that's another big over from Mustafizur
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, SIX runs

Commentary: full on off, and that's been chipped over Powell to long on
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to Holder, 1 run

Commentary: good length outside off, and flicked off his hips to square leg
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full outside off, and worked away to the leg side with soft hands. But they can collect only a single
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to Holder, 1 run

Commentary: good length outside off, and Powell uses his wrists to smother this punch to long on for one
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full outside off, but Holder comes down the wicket and slogs across the line. Off the bat's toe end, and lands juuust short of Shakib at deep midwicket
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to Holder, 1 run

Commentary: good length outside off, but Powell's deceived by the change of pace. Mistimes a punch to long on and gets to fifty!
Commentary_short: Mashrafe Mortaza to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: overpitched on leg stump, and he muscles a shot to short fine leg for a single. Tried to slog it over midwicket, but couldn't get the optimal connection
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full outside off, and Holder is allowed to free his arms. Swings through the ball's line, but the shot goes to long on on the bounce
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to Holder, 1 run

Commentary: full on middle, and Powell clears his front leg to slog across the line. Lifts this with the use of his bottom hand, and the ball goes straight into the cow-corner boundary
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to R Powell, FOUR runs

Commentary: good length on off, and Powell once again makes some room to free his arms. Pulled over to deep midwicket, and a diving effort in the deep may have saved a boundary. But the umpires want to have a second look. Every single run saved counts at this stage.
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to R Powell, 2 runs

Commentary: full on leg stump, and this time the slog goes to deep midwicket on the bounce. Sabbir the man doing the heavy lifting there. Powell's not happy
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full and wide outside off. Holder does well to let it go through. One free run for West Indies
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to Holder, 1 wide

Commentary: full on leg, and Holder's slog is mistimed to deep backward square leg. Eleven off the over
Commentary_short: Shakib Al Hasan to Holder, 1 run

Commentary: full on middle, and he goes for the big shot over extra cover. Can't time it well, and the ball is in the air for ages. Rubel gets under it at long off and does manage to hold on! Sends Holder home.
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Holder, OUT
Dismissal_text: JO Holder c Rubel Hossain b Mustafizur Rahman 9 (10b 0x4 0x6) SR: 90.00

Commentary: full on middle, and defended back to Fizz off the front foot
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, no run

Commentary: lucky! An excellent delivery that costs Fizz a boundary. Back of a length outside leg, and Powell tried to nudge it to the leg side. Takes a leading edge, and flies between keeper and gully!
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, FOUR runs

Commentary: good length ball outside leg stump, and Powell flicks this off his pads to the leg side
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full outside leg stump, and he misses the paddle sweep. Hits the bat's handle and flies away to the off side instead. They appeal for lbw, but the umpire signals runs
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Nurse, 1 run

Commentary: good length on leg stump, and Powell misses the leg-side swipe. Hits his front pad, and the lbw appeal is turned down! Looked much closer, but maybe the height saved him. A chance of a run-out as well, as Mushfiqur has a shy at the stumps with Powell outside his crease. But he misses.
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, no run

Commentary: full outside off, and the drive is drilled to the fielder at cover. All the infielders are on the 30-yard circle
Commentary_short: Rubel Hossain to Nurse, 1 run

Commentary: knee-high full toss but wide outside off. He swings across the line, and gets a good connection too, but the shot goes to long on on the bounce
Commentary_short: Rubel Hossain to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: yorker on off, and shoveled to cover. Just a single
Commentary_short: Rubel Hossain to Nurse, 1 run

Commentary: full outside off, and the slog takes the bat's inside edge! Almost beats the keeper, but Mushfiqur sticks his left hand out and stops the ball. Saves a certain four
Commentary_short: Rubel Hossain to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: attempted yorker on off stump, and all Nurse can do is thump a drive down to long on
Commentary_short: Rubel Hossain to Nurse, 1 run

Commentary: full on off, and Powell can't put this away! It was in the slot to be thumped, but the ball takes an inside edge to the leg side. Powell is disappointed, but atleast he keeps strike
Commentary_short: Rubel Hossain to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: over wide long on! Make that 22 off five! Full on off, and lifted into the stands. In his arc, and Powell doesn't miss out
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, SIX runs

Commentary: good length on leg stump, and the pull goes to deep midwicket. No chance of a double. Gets Nurse on strike
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full outside leg stump, and Nurse's wild swing doesn't make contact with the ball. It goes through to the keeper and now the equation becomes seven runs per ball.
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Nurse, no run

Commentary: good length outside off, and he backs away before cutting to Rubel at cover point. Rubel cartwheels and stops a certain boundary!
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Nurse, 1 run

Commentary: back of a length outside leg, and he flicks it square to deep midwicket
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to R Powell, 1 run

Commentary: full on off, and Nurse brings out a front foot defence to end the series.Bangladesh win by 18 runs!
Commentary_short: Mustafizur Rahman to Nurse, no run
